It's hard enough to learn
various Ethnologue for anthropology.

00:05:15.014 --> 00:05:17.250
But why do we still have to learn English?

00:05:17.250 --> 00:05:20.620
And how come I didn't hear
about the independent report?

00:05:23.389 --> 00:05:26.109
Independent assignment,
a ten-thousand-word reflection.

00:05:26.109 --> 00:05:27.894
The deadline is tomorrow.

00:05:27.894 --> 00:05:29.896
Just kill me.

00:05:52.352 --> 00:05:54.654
Shouldn't dorm mates
take good care of each other?

00:06:20.146 --> 00:06:21.248
What do you want?

00:06:22.215 --> 00:06:24.584
I want to learn from you and study together.

00:06:32.024 --> 00:06:33.192
Help!

00:06:42.235 --> 00:06:44.370
Why didn't you teach me in the library?

00:06:44.370 --> 00:06:46.506
I got nicely dressed.

00:06:47.640 --> 00:06:50.009
You wanted me to read
and translate each section for you.

00:06:50.009 --> 00:06:51.711
Do you think the library is a chanting room?

00:06:52.845 --> 00:06:55.314
I'm not very familiar with English.

00:06:57.016 --> 00:06:58.384
How did you get in then?

00:06:58.885 --> 00:06:59.986
Physical education recommendation.

00:07:04.924 --> 00:07:06.426
You can't break your word.

00:07:06.426 --> 00:07:07.960
I used the one-month bet

00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:09.695
in exchange for your help with this report.

00:07:09.695 --> 00:07:11.464
After this report is submitted tomorrow,

00:07:11.464 --> 00:07:12.899
we'll mind our own business,

00:07:12.899 --> 00:07:14.567
and go on our own separate ways.

00:07:49.936 --> 00:07:52.538
Are these two books the same?

00:07:52.538 --> 00:07:54.674
Why do I feel like they're both the same thing?

00:07:55.374 --> 00:07:57.076
Why don't you write it for me?

00:07:57.076 --> 00:07:59.879
So you don't have to translate it
for me after reading it.

00:07:59.879 --> 00:08:01.814
And I don't have to ask you any questions.

00:08:03.749 --> 00:08:05.051
If I don't hand in this report tomorrow,

00:08:05.051 --> 00:08:06.285
I'll fail this class.

00:08:06.285 --> 00:08:07.820
You can't break the contract.

00:08:07.820 --> 00:08:09.455
Those who break contracts
are worse than pigs and dogs.

00:08:10.957 --> 00:08:12.792
I'm going to the bathroom.

00:08:14.727 --> 00:08:15.895
Go.

00:08:17.530 --> 00:08:19.632
Grab a drink from the fridge on your way?

00:08:43.289 --> 00:08:45.791
Gu, how can you still dare to sleep?

00:08:47.593 --> 00:08:49.729
You have less than fifteen hours left
until you submit the report.

00:09:15.555 --> 00:09:17.440
The teacher said my report
was written very well.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.457
Thanks.

00:09:24.664 --> 00:09:27.266
Put this here. Be careful. Here.

00:09:32.438 --> 00:09:33.873
Xia.

00:09:33.873 --> 00:09:36.809
They didn't mean to scare you.

00:09:36.809 --> 00:09:39.078
Grandpa will seal your ability

00:09:39.579 --> 00:09:42.114
so that don't have to be afraid.

00:09:42.114 --> 00:09:44.717
Grandpa, Senior helped me strengthen it,

00:09:44.717 --> 00:09:46.652
and I've been wearing it all the time.

00:09:46.652 --> 00:09:48.788
You have to continue blessing me and my sister.

00:09:51.023 --> 00:09:52.158
Sis.

