00:10:10.209 --> 00:10:12.311
When I was a child, I was afraid of ghosts.

00:10:12.311 --> 00:10:14.480
You are brave, so the temple is yours.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:16.449
How nice, no one will fight with you.

00:10:16.449 --> 00:10:18.351
I… Eat your ice cream.

00:10:18.351 --> 00:10:19.456
Fine.

00:10:31.631 --> 00:10:32.768
Surrender.

00:10:32.768 --> 00:10:34.667
I won't. Let's see how you can subdue me.

00:10:35.868 --> 00:10:37.703
I'll teach you a lesson.

00:10:37.703 --> 00:10:39.171
Come here. You.

00:10:53.653 --> 00:10:55.988
Burn the talisman.

00:10:55.988 --> 00:10:58.691
Your third eye can be opened,

00:10:58.691 --> 00:11:01.460
