and see ghosts without fear.

00:11:02.828 --> 00:11:05.364
This is our family's responsibility.

00:11:05.998 --> 00:11:08.334
Convey their wishes to their family

00:11:08.334 --> 00:11:10.670
for Grandpa.

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:11.937
Grandpa.

00:11:12.672 --> 00:11:15.541
Today, Senior officially allowed me
to take over the temple.

00:11:18.477 --> 00:11:20.746
As for Buxia,

00:11:20.746 --> 00:11:22.682
since he's so scared,

00:11:22.682 --> 00:11:24.684
we should keep sealing his ability.

00:11:38.230 --> 00:11:41.667
I accidentally burned
a corner of Buxia's talisman.

00:11:41.667 --> 00:11:43.869
It shouldn't be a problem, right?

00:11:43.869 --> 00:11:46.338
Please, Grandpa. Please.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:49.975
Please.

00:12:43.295 --> 00:12:44.797
