How did I end up in bed?

00:16:26.752 --> 00:16:29.272
You were yelling and making a ruckus outside
early in the morning.

00:16:29.272 --> 00:16:30.889
So I dragged your body in here

00:16:30.889 --> 00:16:32.458
from the social hall.

00:16:39.098 --> 00:16:40.566
Grandpa.

